entdb.Rmd) to download the complete source code. Here is the [app](https://scientistcafe.shinyapps.io/shinysample/)\n\n<pre>---\ntitle: \"Customer Segmentation Dashboard\"\noutput: \n  flexdashboard::flex_dashboard:\n    orientation: rows\n    vertical_layout: fill\n    source_code: embed\n    social: menu\n    theme: flatly\nruntime: shiny\n---</pre>\n\n## Some links\n\n- Excellent [Shiny tutorial from beginning to deep level](http://shiny.rstudio.com/tutorial/)\n- [Reactivity Overview](http://shiny.rstudio.com/articles/reactivity-overview.html)\n- [Dashboard Appearance](http://rmarkdown.rstudio.com/flexdashboard/using.html#appearance)",
